<div class='questionText'>
<a href="/questions/1571272-this-book-is-the-first-in-a-series-can-it">This book is the first in a series. Can it be a stand-alone book or should I expect to want to read further?</a>
</div>
<div class='communityQAFooter questionFooter'>
<ul class='questionFooterActions'>
<li class='footerItem like'>
<span class='likeItContainer' id='like_container_community_question_1571272'><a rel="nofollow" class="jsLike like_it" href="https://www.goodreads.com/user/new?remember=true&amp;return_url=%2Fbook%2Fshow%2F43381002-cold-waters">like</a></span>

