<div class='allCommunityAnswers'>
<div class='communityAnswer'>
<div class='communityAnswerBody'>
<div class='answererUserIcon'>
<a class="leftAlignedImage userPhoto" href="/user/show/24129851-debbie-herbert"><img alt="" src="https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/users/1442630483i/24129851._UX100_CR0,15,100,100_.jpg" /></a>
</div>
<div class='communityAnswerTextContainer'>
<span class='communityAnswererName'>
<a href="/user/show/24129851-debbie-herbert">Debbie Herbert</a>
</span>
<span class='communityAnswerText'>
<span class="expandableContainer"><span class="truncatedContent">It is a stand alone as far as the resolution of the characters and their predicaments. The second book in the series has the same setting of Normal, A<a class="jsShow showAction" href="#">…more</a></span><span class="fullContent">It is a stand alone as far as the resolution of the characters and their predicaments. The second book in the series has the same setting of Normal, Alabama but will have new characters.<br /><br />Thanks for asking!<a class="jsHide hideAction" href="#">(less)</a></span></span>
</span>
</div>
