<li class='footerItem like'>
<span class='likeItContainer' id='like_container_community_question_1564531'><a rel="nofollow" class="jsLike like_it" href="https://www.goodreads.com/user/new?remember=true&amp;return_url=%2Fbook%2Fshow%2F43381002-cold-waters">like</a></span>

