<div class='allCommunityAnswers'>
<div class='communityAnswer'>
<div class='communityAnswerBody'>
<div class='answererUserIcon'>
<a class="leftAlignedImage userPhoto" href="/user/show/24129851-debbie-herbert"><img alt="" src="https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/users/1442630483i/24129851._UX100_CR0,15,100,100_.jpg" /></a>
</div>
<div class='communityAnswerTextContainer'>
<span class='communityAnswererName'>
<a href="/user/show/24129851-debbie-herbert">Debbie Herbert</a>
</span>
<span class='communityAnswerText'>
<div class='spoiler'>
This answer contains spoilers…
<span class='spoilerAnswerText'>
<a class="jsShowSpoiler spoilerAction">(view spoiler)</a><span class="spoilerContainer" style="display: none">[
  
    There is no follow up book in regards to Violet and what happens after she leaves Normal. I like to think she does meet Seth again and all is well. I'<a href="#" rel="nofollow noopener">…more</a>
    There is no follow up book in regards to Violet and what happens after she leaves Normal. I like to think she does meet Seth again and all is well. I've written numerous romance novels and strongly believe in happily-ever-afters. :) Hope this helps!<a href="#" rel="nofollow noopener">(less)</a>
  
 <a class="jsHideSpoiler spoilerAction">(hide spoiler)</a>]</span>
</span>
</div>
</span>
